Title : Shot Through the Heart (disambiguation)
Text : '''''[[Shot Through the Heart]]''''' is a film.

'''''Shot Through the Heart''''' may also refer to:

* ''[[Shot Through the Heart (album)|Shot Through the Heart]]'', Jennifer Warnes album
* "[[You Give Love a Bad Name]]" by Bon Jovi, which has "Shot through the heart" as the first line of its chorus.
* "[[Shot Through the Heart (song)|Shot Through the Heart]]", an unrelated song also by Bon Jovi

== See also ==
* "[[Schott Through the Heart]]", an episode of the TV series ''Supergirl''
